t2.github.io/confluent-docs/feed_rss_updated.xml">Confluent</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2025/10/15/3142-confluent-release/</guid> </item> <item> <title>2.1.0 Confluent release</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;2.1.0 Confluent release&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;There is an update to the HPC software stack, bringing xCAT to 2.14.3.lenovo3, based on 2.14.3, and confluent is brought to 2.1.0.&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2018/11/14/210-confluent-release/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 00:47:02 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/feed_rss_updated.xml">Confluent</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2018/11/14/210-confluent-release/</guid> </item> <item> <title>1.8.0 Confluent release</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;1.8.0 Confluent release&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;There is an update to the HPC software stack, bringing xCAT to 2.13.8.lenovo2, based on 2.13.8, and confluent is brought to 1.8.0.&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2018/03/05/180-confluent-release/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 00:47:02 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/feed_rss_updated.xml">Confluent</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2018/03/05/180-confluent-release/</guid> </item> <item> <title>2.0.0 Confluent release</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;2.0.0 Confluent release&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;There is an update to the HPC software stack, bringing xCAT to 2.14.1.lenovo1, based on 2.14.1, and confluent is brought to 2.0.0.&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2018/08/06/200-confluent-release/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 00:47:02 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/feed_rss_updated.xml">Confluent</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2018/08/06/200-confluent-release/</guid> </item> <item> <title>3.0.4 Confluent release</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;3.0.4 Confluent release&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;There is an update to the scale out management stack, bringing xCAT to 2.16.0.lenovo1 (based on 2.16.0) and confluent is now at 3.0.4.&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2020/09/10/304-confluent-release/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 00:47:02 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/feed_rss_updated.xml">Confluent</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2020/09/10/304-confluent-release/</guid> </item> <item> <title>3.3.2 Confluent release</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;3.3.2 Confluent release&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;3.3.2 has been released with the following changes:&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2021/12/15/332-confluent-release/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 00:47:02 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/feed_rss_updated.xml">Confluent</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2021/12/15/332-confluent-release/</guid> </item> <item> <title>Recent Confluent Features</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;Recent Confluent Features&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;Confluent has a new discovery mechanism. This allows for zero-power xCAT style discovery and configuration of lenovo systems.&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2017/12/04/recent-confluent-features/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 17:28:22 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/feed_rss_updated.xml">Confluent</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2017/12/04/recent-confluent-features/</guid> </item> <item> <title>2.2.0 Confluent release</title> <description>&lt;h1&gt;2.2.0 Confluent release&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;p&gt;There is an update to the HPC software stack, bringing xCAT to 2.14.5.lenovo1, based on 2.14.5, and confluent is brought to 2.2.0.&lt;/p&gt;</description> <link>https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2019/04/17/220-confluent-release/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 17:28:22 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/feed_rss_updated.xml">Confluent</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://xcat2.github.io/confluent-docs/release_notes/2019/04/17/220-confluent-release/</guid> </item> </channel> </rss>